edu.uidaho.junicon.runtime.junicon.annotations

Annotation Type MField


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface MField
    Annotation interface for class fields. Bound to the original declared field name.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String name
      Original name of declared field.
      String reifiedName
      Reified name of field.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean isConstructorField
      Is constructor field or local field.
      String type
      Declared type.

    • Element Detail

      • name

        public abstract String name
        Original name of declared field.

      • reifiedName

        public abstract String reifiedName
        Reified name of field. Both original and reified versions exist.

      • type

        public abstract String type
        Declared type.
        Default:
        ""

      • isConstructorField

        public abstract boolean isConstructorField
        Is constructor field or local field.
        Default:
        false
